  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe maintain a \u0022safe harbor\u0022 policy to ensure that exempt individuals are properly classified and paid in accordance with federal and state wage laws, specifically regarding deductions from salary. This policy confirms that improper deductions from an exempt employee\u0027s salary will be corrected, and we will make every effort to avoid such deductions. This helps protect your exempt status and ensures compliance with the Fair Labor Standards Act (FLSA) and similar state laws.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
